The stwuct pewf_event_attw test (attw tests) suppowt
====================================================
This testing suppowt is embedded into pewf diwectwy and is govewned
by the PEWF_TEST_ATTW enviwonment vawiabwe and hook inside the
sys_pewf_event_open function.

The genewaw idea is to stowe 'stwuct pewf_event_attw' detaiws fow
each event cweated within singwe pewf command. Each event detaiws
awe stowed into sepawate text fiwe. Once pewf command is finished
these fiwes awe checked fow vawues we expect fow command.

The attw tests consist of fowwowing pawts:

tests/attw.c
------------
This is the sys_pewf_event_open hook impwementation. The hook
is twiggewed when the PEWF_TEST_ATTW enviwonment vawiabwe is
defined. It must contain name of existing diwectowy with access
and wwite pewmissions.

Fow each sys_pewf_event_open caww event detaiws awe stowed in
sepawate fiwe. Besides 'stwuct pewf_event_attw' vawues we awso
stowe 'fd' and 'gwoup_fd' vawues to awwow checking fow gwoups.

tests/attw.py
-------------
This is the python scwipt that does aww the hawd wowk. It weads
the test definition, executes it and checks wesuwts.

tests/attw/
-----------
Diwectowy containing aww attw test definitions.
Fowwowing tests awe defined (with pewf commands):

